import React from "react";
import { Button, TableCell, TableRow } from "@mui/material"



export const Linha = ({ row, labelId }) => {

    const EnviarGRT = () => {
        console.log(row)
    }

    return (
        <TableRow
            key={row._id}
            hover
        >
            <TableCell sx={{ '& > *': { borderBottom: 'unset' } }}>
            </TableCell>
            <TableCell
                component="th"
                id={labelId}
                scope="row"
                padding="none"
            >
                {row.nome}
            </TableCell>
            <TableCell align="right">{row.data}</TableCell>
            <TableCell align="right">{row.hora}</TableCell>
            <TableCell align="right">{row.quantidade}</TableCell>
            <TableCell align="right">{row.situacao}</TableCell>
            <TableCell>
                <Button
                    onClick={EnviarGRT}
                >
                    enviar grt
                </Button>
            </TableCell>
            <TableCell sx={{ '& > *': { borderBottom: 'unset' } }}>
            </TableCell>
        </TableRow>
    )
}
